672
00:55:50,348 --> 00:55:52,558
Siapa kau?  Kenapa kau di sini?

673
00:55:52,767 --> 00:55:54,935
Pergilah!
Pulang ke rumah!  Enyah!

674
00:55:55,018 --> 00:55:56,437
-Tapi Nona...
